{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534502727&di=a5a259ae8a4d1d28e7869442378fba10&src=http%3A%2F%2Fg.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fdc54564e9258d1094d56039ed958ccbf6c814d61.jpg","summary":"河南警察学院是一所本科层次的普通高等学校，是全国公安系统A等学校。学校前身是1949年2月成立的中共豫西区党委社会部保卫干部训练班；历经河南省公安干部学校、河南省人民警察学校、河南公安高等专科学校等发展时期；2010年3月，经教育部、省政府批准设立河南警察学院。根据2018年4月学校官网显示，学院有三个校区，分别位于郑州、开封和洛阳，占地总面积1690余亩，馆藏纸质图书101万余册；开设12个系(部)、开办16个本科专业、2个专科专业；共有教职工767人，全日制在校生5537人。","tags":["政法类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1949","所在地区":"河南省郑东新区龙子湖高校园区龙子湖东路一号","院校隶属":"河南省"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502727&di=d130b878950b2fa7bfe8322a30364697&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3603561447%2C3958918412%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502727&di=c9129dc38b7a147f269435f6929f9c39&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3630419740%2C891138250%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502727&di=5a976342a4b7b55872c0f42eabd9a7cf&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3609345195%2C737762919%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502727&di=3baea7eeaea7b51080af206db2836f5a&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3573781864%2C3798337321%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502727&di=662192e54c964138e6f7c50a15bb1bfc&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3582313055%2C3923819046%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502727&di=1d71d7cd39311b5ec